<h1>Review Management: How to Handle Negative Airbnb Reviews Professionally</h1>

<h2>Why Do Negative Reviews Matter (And How to Fix Them)?</h2>

<p>A single 1★ review can cost you 10-15% of bookings for months. Guests scan reviews, see that red star, and keep scrolling.</p>

<p>But here's what most hosts don't know: <strong>Negative reviews are often FIXABLE.</strong></p>

<p>At iHousing, we've managed 10,000+ reviews across 100+ properties since 2018. Our average rating is 4.8★. When we do get negative reviews, 80% are successfully resolved or mitigated through professional response strategies.</p>

<p>Here's our complete review management system.</p>

