    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>Key insight:</strong> 90% of negative reviews stem from PREVENTABLE issues (cleanliness, communication, check-in). Only 10% are truly unreasonable guests.</p>

<h2>The Golden Window: First 48 Hours</h2>

<p>When a negative review appears, you have 48 hours to respond. What you do in this window determines whether the review permanently damages your listing or becomes a non-issue.</p>

<h3>Our 48-Hour Response Protocol</h3>

<table class="w-full">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Time Frame</th>
      <th>Action</th>
      <th>Purpose</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
